author: @Datasciencedojo
text: This Introduction to R video series will get you up to speed on R and Programming 101 or programming foundations: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL8eNk_zTBST8j2BU5HYFQogdCjtrHyQAx

author: @chriscockrell9495
text: 0:30 Arithmetic Operators - takes numeric data and makes numeric data. 1:30 Rational Operators - takes data and compares/evaluates an equation, then makes an affirmation.  Is the statement (equation) accurate?  yes or no. 2:00 Logical Operators - conditions for a decision.

author: @UncleLoren
text: This series is a good overview of the R basics. Thank you for posting! One minor point of clarification: the rational operators are actually referred to as *relational* operators.
